**AI usage:** Claude (Anthropic) was used throughout this project as a learning and debugging aid — explaining threading primitives (mutexes, condvars, pthreads), discussing concurrency concepts (deadlock, starvation, Coffman's conditions), helping structure data types and init/cleanup functions, identifying bugs during development, and writing this documentation. All code was hand-written and understood.